{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-tag-tsx","path":"/tags/interviewing/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"jmsbrdy"}},"allMarkdownRemark":{"totalCount":3,"edges":[{"node":{"excerpt":"In the second essay of Women & Power, Mary Beard puts forward the idea that in order to treat women fairly in the workplace (and elsewhere), our priority shouldn’t be to figure out how women can shoulder their way forward and achieve success in the same way as your stereotypical man should. Instead…","fields":{"slug":"/diversity-and-progress-traps/"},"frontmatter":{"date":"May 10, 2020","title":"Diversity as a superpower, and the madness of monocultures","thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":0.810126582278481,"src":"/static/bf97b031e79b97fbe6738ddbbe66d6a6/07af2/blackball.jpg","srcSet":"/static/bf97b031e79b97fbe6738ddbbe66d6a6/684c4/blackball.jpg 64w,\n/static/bf97b031e79b97fbe6738ddbbe66d6a6/6d25d/blackball.jpg 128w,\n/static/bf97b031e79b97fbe6738ddbbe66d6a6/07af2/blackball.jpg 256w,\n/static/bf97b031e79b97fbe6738ddbbe66d6a6/57dc6/blackball.jpg 384w,\n/static/bf97b031e79b97fbe6738ddbbe66d6a6/c17f9/blackball.jpg 505w","sizes":"(max-width: 256px) 100vw, 256px"}}},"staticThumbnail":null}}},{"node":{"excerpt":"I recently came across a discussion on Reddit concerning take-home tests as part of an interview process. It basically boiled down to: Is it acceptable for companies to ask candidates to work on a problem in their own time, so that their submitted solution helps decide whether to move forwards to an on-site interview? The level of antipathy towards take-home tests in that discussion was an enormous surprise. The majority of commenters were not just against the idea, but virulently so, railing against it as another example of unreasonable demands made on candidates. Most people viewed these tests as a waste of time, rude, disrespectful, or a combination of all three. I think there was only one person whose opinion wasn’t negative, and even that was ambivalent at best.","fields":{"slug":"/take-home-tests/"},"frontmatter":{"date":"January 24, 2018","title":"Take Home Tests","thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.4883720930232558,"src":"/static/f701eb7b00b50f27f602efea12ac1672/07af2/blake-connally-373084.jpg","srcSet":"/static/f701eb7b00b50f27f602efea12ac1672/684c4/blake-connally-373084.jpg 64w,\n/static/f701eb7b00b50f27f602efea12ac1672/6d25d/blake-connally-373084.jpg 128w,\n/static/f701eb7b00b50f27f602efea12ac1672/07af2/blake-connally-373084.jpg 256w,\n/static/f701eb7b00b50f27f602efea12ac1672/57dc6/blake-connally-373084.jpg 384w,\n/static/f701eb7b00b50f27f602efea12ac1672/49b36/blake-connally-373084.jpg 512w,\n/static/f701eb7b00b50f27f602efea12ac1672/947df/blake-connally-373084.jpg 5472w","sizes":"(max-width: 256px) 100vw, 256px"}}},"staticThumbnail":null}}},{"node":{"excerpt":"At the moment – and for the foreseeable future – the power balance of hiring\nnegotiations favours the engineering candidates rather than with the hiring\ncompany. One consequence of this is that any attempt to hurry, strong-arm, or\nmanipulate candidates will likely be ineffective, and could potentially\nbackfire horribly. This is how I became one such backfire.","fields":{"slug":"/why-exploding-offers-dont-work/"},"frontmatter":{"date":"February 11, 2015","title":"Why exploding job offers don't work for senior hires","thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.4883720930232558,"src":"/static/5d5371a8b776433ad4205e5a23ba01a4/07af2/explosion.jpg","srcSet":"/static/5d5371a8b776433ad4205e5a23ba01a4/684c4/explosion.jpg 64w,\n/static/5d5371a8b776433ad4205e5a23ba01a4/6d25d/explosion.jpg 128w,\n/static/5d5371a8b776433ad4205e5a23ba01a4/07af2/explosion.jpg 256w,\n/static/5d5371a8b776433ad4205e5a23ba01a4/57dc6/explosion.jpg 384w,\n/static/5d5371a8b776433ad4205e5a23ba01a4/49b36/explosion.jpg 512w,\n/static/5d5371a8b776433ad4205e5a23ba01a4/50587/explosion.jpg 2400w","sizes":"(max-width: 256px) 100vw, 256px"}}},"staticThumbnail":null}}}]}},"pageContext":{"tag":"interviewing"}}}